Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:13.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大富豪　バッテラだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:13.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In the palace, the King has \Ncompleted his recovery, and continues to play Gungi without rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:18.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}目的？　もちろん 『グリードアイランド』ですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:18.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:27.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ですから　愛ですよ　愛。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:27.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Her mind and body are at their limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:35.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}愛するものを独占したいと 思うのは　当然でしょう。 愛とは？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:35.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I estimate it will only take another \Nmatch or two before the King wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:21.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今　何時だ？ あ…　クラピカ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:21.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you can barely sit straight, \Nthe victory won't satisfy me. Recover your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:28.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}半日も…　寝ていたのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:28.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Even while his arm was being treated, \Nthe King never stopped playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:35.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}丸２日だぜ　クラピカ ボスは？　地下競売は？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:35.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But now he changes his mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:38.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}結局　中止になったわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:38.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This female is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:46.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}残りの品は　後日 ネットオークションになるそうよ。 ボスも納得してくれたわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:46.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If this continues, she could prove quite troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:06.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}スクワラが殺されたの。 えっ？ それで　エリザが ひどく取り乱しちゃって。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:06.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then, I will excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ボスは　そのことより
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I must not be too hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:16.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}エリザの動揺ぶりに ショックを受けていたわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:16.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King chose to retract his decree. In order to stay true to his convictions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:22.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それで　自分から 「帰る」って言い出して…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:22.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In order to defeat the Gungi \NChampion at her best...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In order to demonstrate his strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:31.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴンとキルアは？ ２人は元気よ　今頃は…。 寝ちまったよ。 あっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:31.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I kill this girl now, the King will remain a loser at Gungi forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:39.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつらは 自分のやるべきことをやってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:39.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}as someone the King could never defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:51.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}幻のゲーム 『グリードアイランド』です！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:51.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:54.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:54.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My hasty impulse could have left \Nthe King with a permanent scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:18.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お！ ご覧の通り　その不思議な力は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:18.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once I have seen the King conquer the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この中で　誰かが プレーし続けている限り！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Using Knov-san's Apartment Complex, \Nseven people will infiltrate the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:37.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}現在もプレーヤーとして ゲーム内に存在しております。 実は　このゲームは 彼との契約によって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:37.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Shoot and me... Gon, Killua, Meleoron, Ikalgo, and then Morel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:44.36,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}当オークションに 譲渡されたものなのです。 ジンが持って来たんじゃ ないんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:44.36,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A few seconds after us, the Chairman will enter from beyond Pitou's En.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:49.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジェイトサリは　次のような 契約書を残しておりました。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:49.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}During that time, we must draw \Nthe Royal Guard from the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:52.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「本契約書に記載された 年月日までに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:52.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Gon, Killua, and Ikalgo will go in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:59.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}このゲームが クリアされなかった場合 その時点で　私を含めた７名が プレー中であったとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:59.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When we suddenly appear \Nin the midst of the palace, their immediate reaction will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:03.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}無償で　このゲーム７本を ハード機とともに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:03.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}To protect the King with their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}サザンピースオークションに 提供し
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They'll probably use a formation like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:14.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}才能ある後輩に　ゲームクリアの 夢を託すことにする」と。 残念ながら　我々が入手した時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:14.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Breaking it won't be easy. And that's where I come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:33.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでは　９億ジェニーから お願いします！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:33.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:41.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１０億　出ました！ １５億　出ました！ １０５番　倍！　３０億！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:41.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Uh, about Palm... Can we do anything to learn \Nwhat's happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:44.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}７１番　さらに倍！　６０億！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:44.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She's either dead or in hiding. If she'd gotten out, she'd have contacted us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:53.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}挙げた手の形で 金額を表すんだね。 ああ　オークショニアが その中から
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:53.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Since she hasn't, that's the only explanation. If she were captured, \Nshe'd have taken her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:56.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}瞬時に　一番高い額を 発表するんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:56.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When she left, she was prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}じゃあ　これは？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we try to check in on her, \Nit would be an insult to her resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:04.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２０１番　さらに倍！ ２４０億！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:04.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey, you're being too harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:07.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}バカ！　お前！ チッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:07.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Gon's just concerned about Palm. And his concern is worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:14.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はぁ　助かった。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:14.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You just came back! Where do you get off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:21.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうやら　兄貴の野郎 『グリードアイランド』のロムを 解析できなかったらしいな ７１番　２５５億！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:21.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Assuming that Palm was captured alive, it would mean the enemy knows our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:25.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつ！　いくら持ってんだよ フン。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:25.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which would make us like moths \Nflying straight into the flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:29.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１６番 一気にアップで　３０５億です！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:29.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'll be destroyed instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:34.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クッソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:34.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But instead of worrying about worst-case scenarios, what's important is that we trust Palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:47.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フ。 ３０５億…　ですか。 別に構わん。 このゲームをクリアすることが できるのならばな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:47.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, that certainly makes sense, but Gon's point might be that, if Palm has met such a fate, we still \Nhave time to change the plan. Think again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの　俺達 ハンターなんですけど…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He'll say that we have to save Palm first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:54.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}『グリードアイランド』の ゲームクリアに協力しますよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:54.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But he won't offer any plans for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:57.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ふざけてないで さっさと帰りなさい。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:57.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Right? R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:07:02.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ふざけてないよ！ これでもプロハンターなんだ！ 何をバカな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:07:02.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I see your point...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:07.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ライセンスはあるのかね？ はい！ いや　ないよ　まだ質屋だろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:07.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I know you're worried, but once the operation starts, \Nyou'll have to forget her until we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:14.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ　いや　今は…。 ほら見ろ　やっぱりウソか。 ウソじゃ　ないよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:14.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you're distracted for a fraction of a second, that might cause our operation to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:18.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　待ちなさい　この会場に 入れたというだけでも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:18.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We still have two days...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:21.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}君達が特別なのは分かる。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:21.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's still time for Palm to contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:31.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲームクリアを 目指しているのは事実だが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:31.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Nyow I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:38.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プレー人数が 限られているからねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:38.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Should I have tried to escape to the right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:42.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}マズい　作戦失敗か…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:42.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You should have moved your knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:48.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((ぶっちゃけ　ゲームは 買わなくてもいいと思うんだ)) ((欲しいのは ゲームの中の情報！))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:48.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I didn't want to let a single piece \Ncontrol the center of the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:51.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((それに　『グリードアイランド』を 競り落とした人の中にも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:51.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Sometimes, you must accept \Nthe risk and move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:55.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}きっと　プレーヤーを 探している人もいると思うんだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:55.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Otherwise, you won't ever be \Nable to make me hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:04.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プレー人数が限られてる？ １つのカードには　１人分のデータしか セーブできないんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:04.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am unaccustomed to playing a waiting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:10.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}マルチタップを使い　１つのハードで ８人がプレーヤーの上限だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:10.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your Majesty... What is it? I have some sensitive information, \Nso we should step outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:13.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そういえば　メモリーカードの ３０ブロック全部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:13.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's fine, speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:19.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}『グリードアイランド』で 埋まってたよね？ ああ。 なぜ　それを！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:19.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Two days remain until the National Celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:25.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達　『グリードアイランド』の セーブデータを持ってるんです。 君達　プレーしたことがあるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:25.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The number of citizens to process in Peijing \Nhas increased beyond our expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:31.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いえ　データだけ 手に入れたんですけど。 だとしたら　あれも…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:31.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But the weather forecast is favorable, \Nso the selection should proceed as planned. Get to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゲーム機から そのカードを抜くために
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I would like to move up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:39.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう１つ　アイテムが 必要なんだが。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:39.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}the post-selection schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:41.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もしかして！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:41.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's it? Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:46.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの指輪か！ 指輪のことも知っている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:46.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, sir. In that case, we will depart \Nimmediately after the selection— Don't make me repeat myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:52.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうやら　審査対象としての 資格はあるようだねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:52.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm telling you to decide on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:54.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「念」は　使えるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:54.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do not return until I summon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フッ！ フッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, we only need to wait for the King to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:10.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:10.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You think that will only be a \Nfew more matches, right? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:14.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ダメですね プレーさせるだけ無駄です。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:14.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wasn't that what you said a while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:18.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}逃げ回った揚げ句 死ぬのがオチですな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:18.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King is improving at a remarkable rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:21.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やってもみないで　何で分かるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:21.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, she is also evolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:26.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やってからじゃ遅いんだよ　坊や。 死んでくれるのなら　まだいいが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:26.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am no longer able to predict the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:30.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ダラダラと延命されるのが 厄介でな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:30.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, it's still only a matter of \Ntime before the King wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あのゲームは　プレーヤーが 中で生きている限り
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:37.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}リセットも　メモリーカードを 抜くこともできない。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:37.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am. There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:46.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私が雇ったハンターが プロ　アマ含めて １００名ほどプレーしているが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:46.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am one hundred percent confident \Nthat he's acting on his own...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:51.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その半分以上が すでに投げている。 「投げてる」？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:51.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The man who defeated Leol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:54.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}現実世界に戻ることを諦め
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:54.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The reports from Welfin and Brovada confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ずっと　ゲームの中で 生き延びようとしているのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The soldiers under his control \Nare all smoke puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:03.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから 新たなプレーヤーは厳選する。 我々が求めているのは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:03.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Since their complex movements \Nare not typical of Nen puppets, they fooled me as effectively as a smokescreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:12.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最低でも 現実に戻れるアイテムを入手し 帰還できるだけの 力を持つ者だ。 俺達には　その力がないってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:12.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He can't control as many puppets as I can, \Nbut his are more responsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何で　こいつに そんなこと　分かるんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I want to fight him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:17.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それは　彼がプロのハンターで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:17.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I can't leave my post.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:22.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}『グリードアイランド』の 経験者だからだ。 えっ!? えっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:22.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Maybe he'll come to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:32.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}現実帰還のアイテム入手難度は 中の下。 だが　お前達程度の「念」では 入手どころか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:32.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's about time for us to enter Peijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:35.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}すぐに　ゲームオーバーだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:35.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The enemy should have noticed \NMorel's distraction by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:39.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}審査が終われば 俺は　またゲームに戻る。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:39.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'll make some noise in Peijing to negate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:42.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}審査？ あんたが　プレーヤーを 審査するってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:42.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}their belief that this is all the work of one man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:46.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうだ 審査日はオークション最終日。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:46.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}At the same time, many citizens will be moving toward the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:56.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もし　参加する気があるのなら その間　せいぜい 「念」を磨くことだな。 言われなくったってやるよ！ 行こう！　キルア。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:56.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we disappear the day before the celebration, they'll believe assassins are hidden \Namong the citizens, trying to kill the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:11:01.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ところで坊や そのメモリーカードは どうやって入手したんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:11:01.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And their focus will be outside \Nthe palace, on the crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:05.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}教えない！ ハハハ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:05.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's when we enter the palace with \NFour-Dimensional Apartment Complex!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:08.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クッソ！　腹立つなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:08.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King will definitely be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:16.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}絶対　審査　受かってやる！ 審査か…　どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:16.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Watching the selection from \Nthe third-floor throne room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:18.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}聞くまでもないね。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:18.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Will he really be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:45.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カードが１つ ささってるってことは あと１人しか　プレーできねえぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:45.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}2-1-3, pawn. 4-5-1, knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:50.36,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}マルチタップ　使うね。 これで４人　ＯＫね。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:50.36,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}8-7-2, lieutenant general.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:54.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なる で　どっちが先に行く？ 私　行くよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:54.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}4-3-3, archer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:03.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お！　ホントに消えちまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:03.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}As we play, she's getting sharper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}半信半疑だったんだがな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}2-1-1, knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:11.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何？　今の。 ゲームだよ お前らもやらないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:11.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}6-6-1, major general.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:14.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パス。 気が向いたらな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:14.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But it does not pain me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:17.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうか…　じゃ　お先に。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:17.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Rather, I find this enjoyable. Because the board dictates my every move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:27.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}また消えた。 どんなゲームなの？　これ。 実際に死ぬかもしれねえ ゲームだってよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:27.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which proves that she is still \Nseveral levels above me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:30.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}オークションの カタログに書いてある。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:30.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How strong can she become?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ふん。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Supreme Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ　ムカつく！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}言いたい放題 言ってくれちゃって！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう突っかかるなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:56.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そろそろ次の段階を考えても いい頃だってこと。 次の段階？ 「発」…　つまり必殺技さ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:56.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Marvelous moves keep flooding into my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can become even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:01.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカが　「念」を習得したのは 俺達と　ほとんど同じ時期。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:01.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Has she awakened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:04.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}にもかかわらず あいつが　「旅団」と
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:04.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then she's only
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:08.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}対等に戦えるのは 必殺技のおかげ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:08.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}begun to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:16.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　クラピカは「旅団」に対して 無敵に近い能力を得る代わりに 命懸けのリスクを 背負ったんだよね。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:16.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達は　そうはいかない。 うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Could I take a short break?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:24.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}リスクは重過ぎず　軽過ぎず かつ　自分の系統に合ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:24.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's the first time she's asked for a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:34.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}実践的であり　応用の利く そんな能力を考えるんだ。 うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:34.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is something wrong? No, I'd like to return to my room to \Nrecord the moves that are in my mind. But you can't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:37.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　そうなるわな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:37.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, I'll just move the pieces around the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:44.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１つずつ行こうぜ まず　どんな能力にしたいかだな。 「どんな能力に」か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:44.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When I touch the pieces after they're placed, I will never forget their position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:50.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おい　何かあるだろ？ 漠然とでもさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:50.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She's memorized every placement \Nshe's ever experienced? Very well, you're excused.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:52.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　とにかく　すごい能力！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:52.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}漠然とし過ぎ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A foolish question...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:14:00.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}じゃあ　まずは自分の系統から 考えてみようぜ。 ゴンは強化系なんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:14:00.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:04.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やっぱ　何かを強める能力が いいわけだよ。 うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:04.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey. What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:09.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だとすると　次は　お前の何を どう強めるかってことだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:09.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You mean mine? Is there anyone else around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:13.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}痛ったいな！ じゃあキルアは　どうなのさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:13.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's K-K-Komugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}とっくにあるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Komugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:19.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから　お前のほうを 決めようとしてんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:19.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Supreme Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ホント？　どんなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can you please tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:28.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}秘密。 え！ ゴン　俺は今日から 必殺技の特訓に入る。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:28.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}what your name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:30.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まっ　お前は　ゆっくり考えてろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:30.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:34.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もしかしたら　審査には 俺だけ合格しちゃうかもな！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:34.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:43.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつ すぐ横道にそれるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:43.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:50.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}自分のオーラと電気を 融合するイメージ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:50.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, what do you need? Pouf. Yes. Youpi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ　うぅ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is something the matter? Pouf...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:04.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}次は　ためた電力を 一気に放電するイメージで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:04.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Right, you're Pouf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:06.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「念」を練る！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:06.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then... What is my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I speak with utmost respect, Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:17.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((お前達程度の「念」では すぐに　ゲームオーバーだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:17.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You are the King. You have no other name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:20.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クッソ！　絶対　見返してやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:20.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You are the one and only King.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:29.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}熱心だな　ゴン。 クラピカ！　もういいの？ ああ　熱は　下がった もう大丈夫だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:29.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}At the moment, there are impostors \Nusing that name without permission, but we will eliminate them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:34.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全然　大丈夫じゃなさそう でも　クラピカのことだから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:34.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So that the entire world will \Nknow there is only one King.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:37.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「クモ」が　まだヨークシンにいることが 分かったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:37.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That assumes the others can be eliminated. "King" is a title.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:41.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何とか止める方法　ないかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:41.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A title can be bestowed, and it is not a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ところで オークションは　どうだった？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What of you, Youpi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:47.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}高価なゲームを 狙ってるそうじゃないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:47.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your question is far beyond my capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:49.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ　うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:49.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I cannot think of a way to provide an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:59.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なるほど プレーヤー選考審査か。 ねぇ　クラピカは 一体どんな修行をしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:59.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou. I believe that your feelings \Nare what matter most.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:04.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}鎖を具現化しようと思ってからは イメージ修行だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:04.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You should select the name \Nthat you find most pleasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:09.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}目をつぶって　感触を確認したり 何百　何千枚と写生したり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:09.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Very well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:20.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ただ眺めてみたり　舐めてみたり 音や　においも…。 鎖で遊ぶ以外　何もするなと 師匠に言われたからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:20.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can choose a name after the selection. Right now, our priority is to finish all the \Npreparations before tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:23.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しばらくして 鎖を取り上げられた。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:23.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your Majesty, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:27.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうすると　今度は 幻覚で鎖が見えて来るんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:27.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you have any concerns, we shall address them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:31.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その幻覚の鎖に やがて　重たさや冷たさ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:31.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That is why we are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こすれ合う音を感じるようになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Komugi's entire body was glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:38.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうして自然と　具現化した鎖が 出せるようになったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:38.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Komugi? The girl with the closed eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:42.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それ以外は　ゴン達と同じだよ 「纏」と「練」だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:42.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's remembered that human's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She experienced an awakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:52.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ　そうだ　クラピカ！ 俺の師匠になってよ！ クラピカなら　的確に悪いとことか 指摘してくれそうだもん！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:52.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Komugi will now become much stronger, \Nalthough only at Gungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これなら　オークションの間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:57.36,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカを ここに足止めできる！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:57.36,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If Komugi were put through the selection
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:17:00.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}残念だが　それはできない。 えっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:17:00.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that will occur tomorrow, what would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私のボスが 明日にでも　ここをたつ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}She would die. The selection chooses humans
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:09.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}立場上　ついて行かねばならない。 ヨークシンを出るの？ ああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:09.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}with the physical and mental \Nstrength to serve as soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:12.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「クモ」のことは 確かに　心残りだが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:12.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The survivors will be those who demonstrate \Nexcellent combat capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:18.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あれから　すでに２日経った今では もう奴らも　ここには　いまい。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:18.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your Majesty, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:24.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そっか　それがいいよ。 ゴンは　誰に「念」を教わったんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:24.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}After meeting Komugi, I've learned that strength can \Nmanifest in different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:29.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私に聞くより　その人に 聞いたほうがいいんじゃないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:29.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}For example, during our trip here... Your Majesty, please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:34.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハハハ…　必殺技か 君達らしいね。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:34.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}...I killed a child. Your Majesty, you must not say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:39.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}結論から言うと　強化系に 必殺技は必要ありません。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:39.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Perhaps that child...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　何でですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It isn't right... It's inappropriate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:45.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}６つの系統の中で　最も 攻守のバランスがいいからです。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:45.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}...had the potential to surpass \Nme in a certain field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「纏」と「練」を極めて行けば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}An almighty King... Yet I extinguished that potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:51.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが必殺技と呼べるほど すごい威力となる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:51.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}...can never show regret!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　今は　時間がないんです。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I extinguished it for no real reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:59.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうしても俺　４日後の審査に…。 [TEL]　ゴンくん もし　私が審査員で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:59.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You must not say any more! I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:04.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}付け焼き刃の必殺技もどきなど 見せられたら　失望するでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:04.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:20.36,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はい。 マネではなく　今のゴンくんでも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:20.36,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I took a life for no reason at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:26.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}十分　特別な力を 発揮できると思いますよ。 本当!? [TEL]　もちろん！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:26.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What tremendous strength I must possess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:34.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　自分に何ができるかを 一つ一つ思い出してみなさい。 [TEL]　そうすれば おのずと答えは出て来ます。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:34.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I appear with no warning, to rob \Ncountless beings of their inferior strength! To crush... To destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.85,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL] あっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.85,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That is my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:44.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　ヒント　お願い ヒントをください！ 随分　焦ってるみたいですねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:44.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Brute force is the strongest \Npower in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:55.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}期限がなければ 俺も　そう思うんだけど…。 しょうがない　大ヒント！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:55.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am not worthy of being a Royal Guard... Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:19:02.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴンくんが　そのツェズゲラ という人の前で見せたのは 普通の「練」だけでしょう？ [TEL]　うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:19:02.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I jumped to the wrong conclusion, and I nearly insulted the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:11.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今度は　全てを同時に見せなさい。 全てを？ [TEL]　そうです。 [TEL]　いいですか？ 君が覚えたこと全部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:11.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was foolish enough to think that the King \Nmight have regretted his actions...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを同時にです。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You always think too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:21.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}覚えたこと　全てを同時に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:21.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, the King has changed since that girl arrived. Yes, that is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:27.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「纏」　オーラを 肉体の周りにとどめる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:27.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If the girl will impede the King, \Nwe should kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:34.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「絶」　オーラが 全く出ていない状態にする
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:34.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}To think my mind operates \Non the same level as yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:41.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「練」　通常以上の 大量のオーラを生み出す そして　「発」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:41.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes... My power is the strongest that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:46.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}待てよ 「練」は　オーラを出すことで 「絶」は　出さない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:46.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All other power means nothing\N in the face of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:49.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを同時にって…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:49.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They are as dust in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:20:00.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しっかりしろよ　ゴン もたもたしてっと 一気に置いてくぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:20:00.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Her skill is in Gungi, a simple board game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:07.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}無理だよ　出るのと出ないの 同時にやるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:07.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I could turn her into no more than \Na source of meat with the barest touch. So her life depends on my mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:12.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((自分に何ができるかを 一つ一つ思い出してみなさい))
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:12.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I change my mind, I can immediately kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:18.86,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　ウイングさんに 念能力を開発してもらって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:18.86,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then why am I so hesitant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最初は「纏」しか覚えてないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The goal was to kill time while \Nwaiting for the selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}バトルに出ちゃって 大ケガしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The selection is tomorrow... \NHaven't I had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:26.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも そこで「絶」をマスターした
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:26.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I've had my fun. I no longer need her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:31.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それから　ヒソカの技を 見破るために「凝」を覚えて…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:31.34,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do I kill her now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:46.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}集中？　そうだ 気持も目に集中してたから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:46.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Th-Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:50.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}他の部分が　どうなってるか 気づかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:50.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why did you not call for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:53.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}わずかだけど オーラが出てる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:53.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here... And here... You're covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:56.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これを閉じれば 全て同時にできる！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:56.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn, I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よしっ　できた！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't want to bother anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:13.35,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！ ぷは　ダメだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:13.35,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You aren't bothering anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:16.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ちょっと気を抜いただけで 全部　解けちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:16.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What am... You are an important guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:18.84,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　できる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:18.84,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}...I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:23.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これで　もし「練」で増強した オーラを１か所に集中したら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:23.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Didn't I come here to kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:32.33,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:32.33,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why do you cry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:35.34,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}オス！
